This are tools for making maps for UFO2000:
1) Tile Maker,
2) Map Maker.
Both were developed by Nachtwolf in 2006-2007 and published in a thread on official UFO2000 forums and in the bugtracker.
Link to the thread: http://www.xcomufo.com/forums/index.php?showtopic=242025548
Link to the bugtracker issue: http://ufo2000.net/mantisbt/view.php?id=263